  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2793280/extras/c41182916209cb86c9876500f6e7aa6c.poster.avif?t=1711788733\" width=446 height=298 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2793280/extras/c41182916209cb86c9876500f6e7aa6c.webm?t=1711788733\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2793280/extras/c41182916209cb86c9876500f6e7aa6c.mp4?t=1711788733\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Dive into 'Who made this art? Human or AI' – a 2D trivia game where you identify the creator of each masterpiece. Is it a human touch or the brilliance of artificial intelligence? Decide solo or involve your Twitch chat. Unravel the mystery behind each piece – who's the true artist?<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2793280/extras/239c93669e4bd7ee63a4a1a9d069b643.poster.avif?t=1711788733\" width=538 height=358 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2793280/extras/239c93669e4bd7ee63a4a1a9d069b643.webm?t=1711788733\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2793280/extras/239c93669e4bd7ee63a4a1a9d069b643.mp4?t=1711788733\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>With simple but addictive gameplay, in this quiz game you will have less and less time to guess if a artwork was made by an artificial intelligence or by a human, be quick!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2793280/extras/e208d3d5b4b5db369a07fde346adc493.poster.avif?t=1711788733\" width=538 height=356 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2793280/extras/e208d3d5b4b5db369a07fde346adc493.webm?t=1711788733\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2793280/extras/e208d3d5b4b5db369a07fde346adc493.mp4?t=1711788733\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>The online mode is easy to set up, just enter the name of your Twitch channel, the time you want to give your viewers and that's it! Your viewers will only have to enter in the chat the commands !AI or !HUMAN to vote, the one with the most votes at the end of the countdown will be the chosen option. Let's hope your chat has a good eye!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> +1000 different artworks</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Play it live with your Twitch community via chat </li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Beat your scores as an art detective </li></ul>",
  "about_the_game": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2793280/extras/c41182916209cb86c9876500f6e7aa6c.poster.avif?t=1711788733\" width=446 height=298 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2793280/extras/c41182916209cb86c9876500f6e7aa6c.webm?t=1711788733\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2793280/extras/c41182916209cb86c9876500f6e7aa6c.mp4?t=1711788733\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Dive into 'Who made this art? Human or AI' – a 2D trivia game where you identify the creator of each masterpiece. Is it a human touch or the brilliance of artificial intelligence? Decide solo or involve your Twitch chat. Unravel the mystery behind each piece – who's the true artist?<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2793280/extras/239c93669e4bd7ee63a4a1a9d069b643.poster.avif?t=1711788733\" width=538 height=358 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2793280/extras/239c93669e4bd7ee63a4a1a9d069b643.webm?t=1711788733\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2793280/extras/239c93669e4bd7ee63a4a1a9d069b643.mp4?t=1711788733\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>With simple but addictive gameplay, in this quiz game you will have less and less time to guess if a artwork was made by an artificial intelligence or by a human, be quick!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2793280/extras/e208d3d5b4b5db369a07fde346adc493.poster.avif?t=1711788733\" width=538 height=356 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2793280/extras/e208d3d5b4b5db369a07fde346adc493.webm?t=1711788733\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2793280/extras/e208d3d5b4b5db369a07fde346adc493.mp4?t=1711788733\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>The online mode is easy to set up, just enter the name of your Twitch channel, the time you want to give your viewers and that's it! Your viewers will only have to enter in the chat the commands !AI or !HUMAN to vote, the one with the most votes at the end of the countdown will be the chosen option. Let's hope your chat has a good eye!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> +1000 different artworks</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Play it live with your Twitch community via chat </li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Beat your scores as an art detective </li></ul>",
